from my speech before we go.

01:24:10.378 --> 01:24:12.379
"We must not give in
to the fear.

01:24:12.547 --> 01:24:15.299
We must face
those things we fear the most.

01:24:15.467 --> 01:24:17.801
We must appeaI
to our better angels."

